OL,5, Low-income pensioners entitled to      
OL,6, pension credit are being urged to claim
OL,7, it or risk missing out on an extra     
OL,8, cost-of-living payment.                
OL,10,FThe government says those making a new 
OL,11,Fclaim in the next 10 days could get a  
OL,12,Fcost-of-living payment worth #301.     
OL,14,FHundreds of thousands of people who are
OL,15,Feligible for pension credit do not     
OL,16,Fclaim it.                              
OL,18,FThis means they do not receive a top-up
OL,19,Fof the state pension, as well as other 
OL,20,Fpayments and discounts.                
